48
00:05:07.265 --> 00:05:08.266 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
Just, some things happened,

49
00:05:08.349 --> 00:05:11.185 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
