who would smoke those odd cigarettes

279
00:15:54.745 --> 00:15:55.746 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
with that distinctive smell.

280
00:15:55.829 --> 00:15:58.499 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
So they do have a distinctive smell?

281
00:15:58.582 --> 00:16:00.876 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
I always thought it had
a nice, sweet scent.

282
00:16:00.960 --> 00:16:02.419 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
Really?

283
00:16:02.503 --> 00:16:05.172 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
But these aren’t Yasu’s. They’re Shin’s.

284
00:16:05.255 --> 00:16:06.548 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
I confiscated them from him.

285
00:16:06.632 --> 00:16:09.718 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
Huh? What is it with Shin?

286
00:16:09.802 --> 00:16:12.054 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
There’s no sense in me holding onto them,

287
00:16:12.137 --> 00:16:13.138 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
so go ahead and smoke them, Nana.

288
00:16:13.222 --> 00:16:16.141 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
No, I don’t care for these.

289
00:16:16.225 --> 00:16:18.978 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
Leave them here,
and Yasu will smoke them when he’s here.

290
00:16:19.061 --> 00:16:21.230 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
Wait a minute. When did you see Shin?

291
00:16:22.690 --> 00:16:24.441 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
I bumped into him
when I was coming home from work.

292
00:16:24.525 --> 00:16:26.485 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
Oh?

293
00:16:26.568 --> 00:16:30.948 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<i>What am I doing lying to her?</i>
<i>I should just tell her the truth.</i>

294
00:16:31.031 --> 00:16:34.660 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
There’s something fishy here.
Don’t go after Shin.

295
00:16:34.743 --> 00:16:37.496 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
To him, a working woman is
a woman to get money from,

296
00:16:37.579 --> 00:16:38.455 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
even if that woman is you.

297
00:16:38.539 --> 00:16:40.332 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
It’s nothing like that.

298
00:16:40.416 --> 00:16:42.167 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
Then that’s fine.

299
00:16:43.711 --> 00:16:45.462 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
By the way, did you call Misato?

300
00:16:46.672 --> 00:16:49.008 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<i>It was with the first set of members,</i>
<i>back when Ren was in the band.</i>

301
00:16:49.091 --> 00:16:49.925 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
Yeah.

302
00:16:50.009 --> 00:16:52.219 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
I wonder if she got back all right.

303
00:16:52.302 --> 00:16:54.930 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
Mm-hmm. She said she was
on the train on her way home.

304
00:16:55.597 --> 00:16:56.682 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
I’m glad to hear that.

305
00:17:01.979 --> 00:17:04.064 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
You know, Nana, about Ren of Trapnest…

306
00:17:04.148 --> 00:17:06.650 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
This is about the live concert, right?
Sure. I’ll go.

307
00:17:08.360 --> 00:17:09.695 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
Huh? Why?

308
00:17:09.778 --> 00:17:12.197 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
I told you I’d go if I felt like it.

309
00:17:12.281 --> 00:17:13.824 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
So what made you feel like going?

310
00:17:13.907 --> 00:17:16.201 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
No reason. Just felt like it.

311
00:17:16.285 --> 00:17:17.244 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
But…

312
00:17:17.327 --> 00:17:20.164 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
What? If you have plans
with someone else, that’s fine with me.

313
00:17:20.247 --> 00:17:22.207 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
N-- No, let’s go together.

314
00:17:22.291 --> 00:17:24.334 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
I’d be super happy to go with you, Nana.

315
00:17:26.503 --> 00:17:30.090 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<i>Why? Does she want to see Ren after all?</i>

316
00:17:31.258 --> 00:17:34.094 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<i>Maybe she still has feelings for Ren.</i>

317
00:17:35.095 --> 00:17:38.348 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<i>I want to ask her,</i>
<i>but I mustn’t be hasty about it.</i>

318
00:17:38.432 --> 00:17:40.893 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<i>Even if I ask, Nana’s not likely</i>
<i>to be direct with me.</i>

319
00:17:40.976 --> 00:17:42.895 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<i>She won’t give me an honest answer.</i>

320
00:17:43.520 --> 00:17:44.521 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<i>She’ll get embarrassed and say</i>

321
00:17:44.605 --> 00:17:47.399 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<i>she’s changed her mind</i>
<i>about going to the live concert with me.</i>

322
00:17:48.400 --> 00:17:50.569 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:10.00% 
<i>I wonder if I should ask her</i>
<i>after the live concert.</i>

323
00:17:51.320 --> 00:17:53.405 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<i>This is a golden opportunity for them</i>
<i>to get back together.</i>

324
00:17:53.489 --> 00:17:56.158 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<i>If I don’t watch it, I could ruin things.</i>

325
00:17:57.618 --> 00:17:58.786 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<i>We have first row seats.</i>

326
00:17:59.661 --> 00:18:03.373 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<i>The concert hall is small.</i>
<i>Ren will surely notice Nana there.</i>

327
00:18:04.041 --> 00:18:07.795 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<i>The girl he had a tearful break up with</i>
<i>will suddenly be standing before him.</i>

328
00:18:07.878 --> 00:18:09.838 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<i>Ren won’t be able to resist</i>
<i>getting closer to her!</i>

329
00:18:10.756 --> 00:18:12.841 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<i>They will silently look</i>
<i>in each other’s eyes.</i>

330
00:18:12.925 --> 00:18:14.927 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<i>Nana’s eyes will be filled with tears.</i>

331
00:18:15.010 --> 00:18:15.844 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<i>Without a second thought,</i>

332
00:18:15.928 --> 00:18:18.806 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<i>Ren will jump down from the stage</i>
<i>and embrace Nana.</i>

333
00:18:19.389 --> 00:18:20.599 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<i>Beautiful!</i>

334
00:18:21.308 --> 00:18:24.311 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<i>I should keep quiet,</i>
<i>so Nana doesn’t change her mind.</i>

335
00:18:24.394 --> 00:18:27.856 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<i>At least until the concert. I’ll do it.</i>
<i>I’ll act as if don’t know anything.</i>

336
00:18:27.940 --> 00:18:29.149 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<i>I am an adult after all.</i>

337
00:18:29.233 --> 00:18:31.610 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:10.00% 
<i>For the sake of an exciting reunion.</i>

338
00:18:32.444 --> 00:18:34.863 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
Sure. I’ll go along with your story.

339
00:18:34.947 --> 00:18:37.032 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
I acted like I didn’t know
until now anyway.

340
00:18:37.116 --> 00:18:38.534 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
Thank you, Shin!

341
00:18:38.617 --> 00:18:40.452 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
But I envy you.

342
00:18:40.536 --> 00:18:42.871 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
First row seats, right?
I’d like to come too.

343
00:18:42.955 --> 00:18:44.998 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
Yeah, I’m sure you would. I’m sorry.

344
00:18:45.082 --> 00:18:49.169 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
But I wonder if the reunion will be
as exciting as you’re thinking, Hachi.

345
00:18:49.253 --> 00:18:52.548 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
Well, I agree maybe imagining him
jumping off the stage is a stretch.

346
00:18:52.631 --> 00:18:57.177 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
Still, I wonder
if Ren still thinks about Nana.

347
00:18:57.261 --> 00:18:59.138 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
They haven’t been in touch
for two years, right?

348
00:18:59.221 --> 00:19:03.475 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
Yeah. I wonder about that.
To start with, that guy…

349
00:19:03.559 --> 00:19:05.144 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
"To start with that guy," what?

350
00:19:05.227 --> 00:19:07.146 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
Rumor has it he’s a real womanizer.

351
00:19:07.229 --> 00:19:08.063 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
Really?

352
00:19:08.147 --> 00:19:11.733 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
Well, but that’s something from his past.

353
00:19:11.817 --> 00:19:14.695 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
As far as Nana was concerned,
he was very faithful to her.

354
00:19:14.778 --> 00:19:17.823 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
Oh, and that necklace
Ren’s always wearing?

355
00:19:17.906 --> 00:19:20.033 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
Nana gave that to him.

356
00:19:20.117 --> 00:19:21.326 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
No way, really?

357
00:19:21.410 --> 00:19:23.203 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
That’s a totally good sign
he still has feelings for her!

358
00:19:23.287 --> 00:19:24.705 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
But maybe he just likes it,

359
00:19:24.788 --> 00:19:26.790 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
and there’s no real reason
behind him wearing it.

360
00:19:26.874 --> 00:19:28.292 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
That can’t be.

361
00:19:28.375 --> 00:19:31.920 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
It definitely means something to him.
Hey, Yasu, don’t you agree?

362
00:19:34.089 --> 00:19:36.091 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
Yeah, I do.

363
00:19:36.175 --> 00:19:37.926 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
I knew it!

364
00:19:40.846 --> 00:19:41.847 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
What’s the matter?

365
00:19:41.930 --> 00:19:44.933 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
Come on, everyone, practice time.
Let’s give it our best today too.

366
00:19:45.017 --> 00:19:47.436 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
That dampens the mood.

367
00:19:48.270 --> 00:19:50.981 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<i>That was two weeks</i>
<i>before the live concert.</i>

368
00:19:51.064 --> 00:19:52.774 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<i>As my heart pounded</i>

369
00:19:52.858 --> 00:19:54.860 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<i>worrying about the possibility</i>
<i>of Nana changing her mind,</i>

370
00:19:54.943 --> 00:19:57.905 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<i>my imagination just kept escalating.</i>

371
00:19:58.572 --> 00:20:00.991 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<i>If Nana and Ren got back together,</i>

372
00:20:01.074 --> 00:20:02.242 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<i>would that mean members of Trapnest</i>

373
00:20:02.326 --> 00:20:04.244 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<i>could come visit us at our place?</i>

374
00:20:04.995 --> 00:20:07.748 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<i>Then maybe I could become</i>
<i>all lovey-dovey with Takumi.</i>

375
00:20:07.831 --> 00:20:10.167 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
What am I gonna do?

376
00:20:11.501 --> 00:20:12.753 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
What’s the matter, Ms. Komatsu?

377
00:20:35.651 --> 00:20:36.485 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
Yes.

378
00:20:36.568 --> 00:20:38.779 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<i>It’s me.</i>

379
00:20:41.031 --> 00:20:42.532 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
You again?

380
00:20:43.200 --> 00:20:45.494 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
What do you want this late at night?

381
00:20:47.537 --> 00:20:49.081 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<i>The morning of the live concert, Nana,</i>

382
00:20:49.164 --> 00:20:54.002 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<i>you were sitting by that window,</i>
<i>the same as always.</i>

383
00:20:55.170 --> 00:20:58.257 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<i>But there was a different scent</i>
<i>in the room,</i>

384
00:20:59.508 --> 00:21:01.760 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<i>the scent of Black Stone,</i>

385
00:21:02.302 --> 00:21:03.512 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<i>those cigarettes I confiscated from Shin</i>

386
00:21:03.595 --> 00:21:05.847 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<i>that you said you don’t care for.</i>

